  "2026-07-15T09:27:07.658Z",codex-root,"Duplicate check evidence 2026-07-15: all-status search for dependency updates vulnerabilities outdated packages found only closed historical refresh items,chiefly pm-a2g6; no active July 15 dependency-refresh item exists. Live pnpm audit reports zero vulnerabilities and Dependabot reports zero open alerts. pnpm outdated reports safe patch/minor candidates plus major TypeScript,Node types,and unicorn migrations that require compatibility proof."
  "2026-07-15T20:06:31.807Z",codex-audit-20260715,"Review pass 91 dependency evidence from pnpm outdated: remaining current candidates include Vitest and coverage 4.1.10, jscpd 5.0.12, tsx 4.23.1, Sentry 10.65, ESLint 10.7, sonarjs 4.2, Greptile 3.2, typescript-eslint 8.64, @types/node 26.1.1, eslint-plugin-unicorn 71.1, and TypeScript 7.0.2. pnpm audit reports zero advisories across 330 dependencies. Preserve the existing compatibility-matrix and batched-upgrade scope."
  "2026-07-19T16:15:16.797Z",codex-wide-sdk-20260719,"2026-07-19 dependency snapshot: pnpm audit reports 0 vulnerabilities across 341 dependencies. Remaining outdated candidates are @toon-format/toon 2.3.0 to 2.3.1, greptile 3.2.0 to 3.2.2, @sentry/node 10.65.0 to 10.66.0, eslint-plugin-sonarjs 4.1.0 to 4.2.0, eslint-plugin-unicorn 71.1.0 to 72.0.0, and TypeScript 6.0.3 to 7.0.2. Preserved this canonical open upgrade lane; no duplicate and no unrelated dependency churn in the current PR."
