  "2026-07-15T19:27:05.225Z",maintainer-agent,"pnpm outdated snapshot 2026-07-15 (review pass #89): patch/minor — @vitest/coverage-v8+vitest 4.1.9→4.1.10, jscpd 5.0.11→5.0.12, tsx 4.23.0→4.23.1, @sentry/node 10.63.0→10.65.0, eslint 10.6.0→10.7.0, eslint-plugin-sonarjs 4.1.0→4.2.0, greptile 3.1.1→3.2.0, typescript-eslint 8.62.1→8.64.0. MAJORS needing compatibility proof — @types/node 22.20.1→26.1.1 (engines floor is >=22.18, types should track the floor, likely stay on 22.x or bump floor decision), typescript 6.0.3→7.0.2 (gate + build + type-strip loader proof), eslint-plugin-unicorn 70.0.0→71.1.0 (rule churn vs eslint-suppressions.json A+ baseline). Majors are each their own gate-proof commit; never bundle with patch sweeps."
  "2026-07-17T05:13:54.812Z",maintainer-agent,"Dependency snapshot advanced 2026-07-17 (user-directed dependabot triage, pass #94): MERGED to main — dev-deps group #572 (@vitest/coverage-v8+vitest 4.1.10, eslint 10.7.0, greptile 3.2.0, jscpd 5.0.12, tsx 4.23.1, typescript-eslint 8.64.0), eslint-plugin-unicorn 71.1.0 (#541), @sentry/node 10.65.0 (#538), @types/node 26.1.1 (#540 — required the SetIterator annotation fix in src/core/extensions/item-fields.ts; frozen ReadonlySet wrappers must return SetIterator under the node-26 libs). NOT adopted: typescript 7.0.2 (#539) — closed via dependabot major-version ignore; migration owned by pm-do5b (typescript-eslint peer <6.1.0 + no stable JS compiler API for static-quality-gate.mts). Remaining majors from the #89 snapshot: TS7 only (types/node 26 now DONE)."
